.\" Manpage for icount.

.\" Contact "our emails here" to correct errors or typos.

.TH man 1 "10 Nov 2015" "0.1" "icount man page"

.SH NAME
icount \- count file descriptors

.SH SYNOPSIS
icount -[rdlbcav] \fBpathname\fB

.SH DESCRIPTION
icount returns the number of file descriptors, of a certain type, that are open in the pathname.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-r
Set the file type of the search for descriptors open to regular.
Cannot be used with options d, l, b, c.
.TP
.BR \-d
Set the file type of the search for descriptors open to directory.
Cannot be used with options r, l, b, c.
.TP
.BR \-l
Set the file type of the search for descriptors open to link.
Cannot be used with options r, d, b, c.
.TP
.BR \-b
Set the file type of the search for descriptors open to block.
Cannot be used with options r, d, l, c.
.TP
.BR \-c
Set the file type of the search for descriptors open to character.
Cannot be used with options r, d, l, b.
.TP
.BR \-a
Set icount to count hidden files.
Can be used with options r, d, l, b, c, v.
.TP
.BR \-v
Set verbose mode
Can be used with options r, d, l, b, c, a.

.SH SEE ALSO
.BR

.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
